name: Zinnia Resiliency 🌼 (Disaster Recovery)
description: "We've had a major disaster and we're takin' it like normal American people: trying to do our best. What else can you do?" Part of a series investigating hope and progress in the aftermath of disaster. Archival media clip from "Welcome To Corning, New York: Tropical Storm Agnes Flood" by the Federal Emergency Management, 1972. [ 1080x1350px | 4:5 | 330 frames | 11 seconds ]
